// =============================================================================
// PRAGMA journal_mode — one of DELETE / TRUNCATE / PERSIST / MEMORY / WAL / OFF.
// Switching to WAL is persistent across sessions; switching back to a non-WAL
// mode is also persistent.  MEMORY/OFF are connection-local for non-persistent
// databases; for file-backed they're rejected or short-lived.
// Spec §15.4 + §18.4.
// =============================================================================

module core.database.sqlite.native.journal_mode_pragma_api;

public module mode_;
